title: Do new Malzahar's voidlings apply on-hit effects?
body: I'm gonna buy malzahar to be my new midlane champ and i was thinking about playing him in the jungle occasionally, but only if his voidlings apply on-hit effects. I was just curious to see if they do since if its true then i was gonna play him ad bloodrazor jg.

replies.body: they apply rylai and liandry and omnivamp from gunblade
